    <text>
        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>15<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Augt./59</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Pha</p>
            <p>Rev. DrSir!</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Your esteemed Letter<lb/> I duly received and communicated<lb/> its
                contents—in as far as they<lb/> concern him—to <persName>Mr Benjamin</persName><lb/>
                who intends to write to you<lb/> direct.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">In consequence of your<lb/> remarks, I got the Israelite<lb/> and
                read the article in<lb/> question. It is, as usual a<lb/> gross fraud, &amp; an
                impudent<lb/> speculation on the ignorance<lb/> of the public. I hold the<lb/> man
                &amp; his paper in too<lb/> great contempt to be<lb/> moved by any thing he</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>writes. Still we have a<lb/> public duty to perform to the<lb/> illustrious dead, and
                must<lb/> not permit the Israelite to<lb/> claim fellowship with
                Rambam<add>?</add>.<lb/> I will therefore send you<lb/> in the course of this
                week—say<lb/> on <date>Wednesday</date> or <date>Thursday</date>—a<lb/> paper on
                “Jewish doctrine”<lb/> “<persName>Maimonides</persName> on a future<lb/> state,
                Repentance, and the<lb/> resurrection of the dead”<lb/> which I trust, in
                addition<lb/> to disposing of the “Israelite” will<lb/> have the merit of a word
                in<lb/> season for the <add>ימים הנוראים הבע"ל</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I shall want a Bible<lb/> to give away. What is the<lb/> very lowest
                price for a copy<lb/> plainly bound.?[sic]</p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p rend="indent(1)">If you think well of the<lb/> paper I am about to send<lb/> you try
                to get it inserted<lb/> into some <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName> paper<lb/> I
                myself will take charge of<lb/>
                <placeName>St Louis</placeName>—formerly one of the<lb/> “Israelites” strongholds,
                but<lb/> where now thank God his<lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">prestige</hi> is gone</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Yours very respfy</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <persName role="author">M J Raphall</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p>
                <add>?</add>
            </p>
            <pb n="Envelope"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Revd Isaac L</addressee>
                <add>?</add>
            </p>
            <p>Office of the Occident</p>
            <p>
                <placeName>No 1227. Late 371 Walnut Street</placeName>
            </p>
